<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0078d7;
            color: white;
            font-family: Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 50px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .sad-face {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .progress {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #005a9e;
            height: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 20%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .qr-code {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background-color: white;
            margin-top: 30px;
            opacity: 80%;
        }
        .small-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="sad-face">:(</div>
        <h1>Your page ran into a problem and couldn't be found.</h1>
        <p>We're just collecting some error info, and then we'll redirect you to our homepage.</p>
        <div class="progress">
            <div class="progress-bar"></div>
        </div>
        <p>20% complete</p>
        <img class="qr-code" src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://linktr.ee/swarooppatilx">
        <p>For more information about this issue and possible fixes, visit<br>https://github.com/swarooppatilx</p>
        <p class="small-text">If you call a support person, give them this info:<br>
        Stop code: PAGE_NOT_FOUND<br>
        What failed: requested_url</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>